  "title": "Facilities Officer",
  "description": "<p>Duties:</p><p><ul><li>Manage the receipt, storage and issuance of engineering and facilities materials, equipment, tools and critical spare parts</li><li>Maintain accurate inventory records and stock levels using digital systems or manual logs, and conduct regular stock checks to identify low or expired items</li><li>Coordinate with procurement teams and vendors to ensure timely replenishment of essential materials</li><li>Support daily facility inspections, basic troubleshooting and first-level fault identification and reporting</li><li>Monitor, record and document key operational readings from building and engineering systems such as temperature, pressure and flow rates</li><li>Assist in implementing workplace safety controls during maintenance and contractor activities, including Permit-to-Work and lock-out/tag-out procedures</li><li>Ensure work areas are maintained in a safe condition and support safety drills, inspections and audits</li><li>Report near-miss incidents or safety concerns and follow up on corrective actions</li><li>Assist with the installation, setup and testing of new equipment or facility infrastructure</li><li>Maintain facility documentation including maintenance logs, checklists, PTW forms and service reports</li><li>Assist contractors and vendors on site and ensure compliance with site safety and operational requirements</li><li>Carry out minor repairs, fixture replacements and workspace setup tasks as required</li><li>Respond to facility fault reports such as power trips, HVAC issues and system alarms</li><li>Support general facility operations including housekeeping, waste management and pest control coordination<br /></li></ul></p><p>Requirements:</p><p><ul><li>Min Nitec in Mechanical, Electrical, Facilities or Building Services Engineering.</li><li>Min 2 years of relevant experience in technical facility operations.<br /></li></ul></p><p>Interested Applicants, please click Apply Now<br /></p><p>Chow Zi Qing<br />R2199258<br />Revup Proservices Pte Ltd<br />EA.24C2366</p>",
